[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    182[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **The problem:** "Minimum 1,000 interactions per message type for reasonable model quality. Synthetic data acceptable for development." This reads slightly clinical/documentation-voice compared to the rest of the recipe. The rest of the recipe would say something like "You need at least 1,000 interactions per message type before the model learns anything useful. Synthetic data works fine for development."
